Dr. Suchismita treated my 81-yr old mom in a very critical state, just out of the ICU and in ward, with a multitude of complex problems including heart, lung infection, kidney malfunctions and so on. She takes a holistic and symptomatic approach and is very positive and reassuring rather than giving up on my mom at all, because of her age and multiple complications. She has great intuitions that come from experience, and a great attitude that comes from a unique combination of confidence and humility. I will go to her for any general medicine issues for my entire family and would recommend her to all my friends too.
